  "title": "[ICON Aesthetics] Aesthetician / Beautician / Beauty Therapist",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Perform aesthetic treatments for customers</li><li>Perform aesthetic treatments with high standards of customer service</li><li>Perform skin/body/hair analysis for new and existing customers</li><li>Makes professional recommendations on products, treatments and packages to customers</li><li>Exposure to a diverse range of aesthetic treatments including skin, face, body, slimming, hair removal, hair growth, teeth whitening etc</li><li>Handle customers' requests and enquiries when necessary</li><li>Various sponsored training programs and skill upgrading courses available for outstanding performance</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Prior experience in beauty / aesthetics / spa industry as a beautician, therapist or aesthetician</li><li>With a friendly personality.</li><li>Good communications and interpersonal skills, and service attitude.</li><li>Effectively bilingual</li><li>Able to start work with short notice</li><li>Work location at Orchard</li></ul><p>6 off days in a month, 10 days annual leave and other leave perks.</p><p><br /></p><p>High commission with many incentive schemes to achieve your desired salary goals.</p><p><br /></p><p>In-house mentoring and training provided to prepare you for an award-winning aesthetics environment.</p><p><br /></p><p>Good employment benefits including medical reimbursements, dental benefit, attendance rewards, KPI incentives, health and wellness incentives, insurance coverage and more!</p><p><br /></p><p>Join us today!</p>",
